{"tid":638441,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"心地善良有樣睇","createTime":"2018-04-22T17:15:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-22T17:54:37.000Z","uid":27793,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"8934d0f9f7115db28fff99aa76f90a5c68a32c46","tid":638441,"uid":27793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T17:15:26.000Z","msg":"個樣係真係忠厚啲<br />\n感覺正氣<br />\n無論細眼定大眼"},{"pid":"7ca5e2610309f4d698bdea2129ed26a290d740da","tid":638441,"uid":27793,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T17:16:44.000Z","msg":"啱啱俾個細+斜眼佬跣咗鑊<br />\n佢成撚日都奸笑咁款"},{"pid":"68b8b45b4454b4e9d3c5b328b82bd944a7058690","tid":638441,"uid":27793,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T17:20:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.japhub.com/201605/46xmmoJR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.japhub.com%2F201605%2F46xmmoJR.jpg&h=23596350&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n連動畫都畫到奸人係咁<br />\n笑容 眉頭眼額<br />\n其實真係feel到個人係奸定忠<br />\n一定程度"},{"pid":"5ad2f3fe09f91299ad71e1c1f22e01d8031ec83b","tid":638441,"uid":165024,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"68b8b45b4454b4e9d3c5b328b82bd944a7058690","tid":638441,"uid":27793,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T17:20:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.japhub.com/201605/46xmmoJR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.japhub.com%2F201605%2F46xmmoJR.jpg&h=23596350&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n連動畫都畫到奸人係咁<br />\n笑容 眉頭眼額<br />\n其實真係feel到個人係奸定忠<br />\n一定程度"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T17:29:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/23/012901_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F23%2F012901_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=bef58fe7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d200b4dd593c4761e1d43cb8e384dc9479b1b3c9","tid":638441,"uid":27793,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T17:29:13.000Z","msg":"真係小撚心呢啲同事<br />\n面相呢家嘢 真係寧可信其有 <br />\n<br />\n成日都笑笑口<br />\n但對眼永遠向上吊咁<br />\n得個嘴假笑<br />\n眼附近啲肌肉唔識笑<br />\n平時最鍾意扮君子 好有禮貌咁款<br />\n<br />\n請各位要相信自己直覺<br />\n（我啱啱踏入社會就俾呢啲撚樣出賣）<br />\n唉 只能說要相信自己直覺<br />\n第一眼覺得唔妥 可能真係唔妥"},{"pid":"55efc4c85e9635daee53c93e334946e3eac64e3c","tid":638441,"uid":68215,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T17:54:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/c/c6/他永遠對著你笑.gif/revision/latest?cb=20161227100201\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2Fc%2Fc6%2F%E4%BB%96%E6%B0%B8%E9%81%A0%E5%B0%8D%E8%91%97%E4%BD%A0%E7%AC%91.gif%2Frevision%2Flatest%3Fcb%3D20161227100201&h=ec16fd96&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}